headline: Prologis (PLD) To Add 4000 Homes with Caltrain Site Revamp
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE:PLD) is one of the most undervalued stocks. Prologis recently indicated its intention to file redevelopment plans later this year for the Caltrain railyards located at Fourth and King Street.
